name: CULL
description:
Cull is a 2D pixel art, hack 'n' slash, highscore hunting game about a proud warrior who was betrayed and killed by his own people.... reborn..... undead, you now fight endlessly throughout hell gathering heads and drenching yourself in blood to fulfill this vengeance inside you.

Features :
  • Fun and enjoyable game play
  • Highscores
  • Infinite waves of enemies
  • Great Pass time game
  • not a game for the weak of heart
Minimun System Requirements :
  • OS : Windows XP, Vista or higher
  • Processor : 2.0GHZ
  • Memory : 1 GB RAM
  • Graphics : 256MB
  • DirectX : Version 7.1
  • Storage : 35 MB available space
